# pyqt-font-dialog

PyQt Font Dialog



## Requirements

PyQt5 >= 5.8



## Setup

`python -m pip install pyqt-font-dialog`



## Usage

```python

dialog = FontDialog(textEdit.currentFont())

reply = dialog.exec()

if reply == QDialog.Accepted:

    textEdit.setCurrentFont(dialog.get_font())

```



